name: Zagger Shkeet - transmission
description:
A character from my upcoming Graphic Novel Series, Veil Of The Gods. 


Zagger Shkeet is the pseudonym of a prominent leader of the Idealist Front after the success of the Communard Coup that overturned the monarchy in the former Kingdom of Kusht. Though trained as a Priestess of Tesh, she rejected the Materialist teachings of the White Jattamansi and turned against her mentors. Her mastery of transmission technology is renowned, and she is highly respected by all the resistance groups of Kusht. Her true identity is the subject of intense speculation.

Art & music by Ziggetai
